recipeInstructions.text: Place the sweet potato wedges in a large bowl, add the oil, garlic powder, smoked paprika, cornflour and black pepper and toss well to coat.
Heat the air fryer to 200Â°C and spread the wedges out in a single layer. Cook for 20 minutes, shaking halfway through. Repeat with the second batch and serve.
